{
  "stem": "24195.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So-- and they had-- they had the air-raid wardens that they were-- so I don't know how I got a helmet, a regular steel helmet, from one of those air-raid wardens.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I put them-- and I put them up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And my mother said--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Why don't you stand at the end?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They have, yeah, they have-- no, not the-- it had no swastika.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was just an-- it was just a regular, plain helmet.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the air-raid wardens used them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I don't know how I got it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I, I stayed the-- and I tried to stand guard at the entrance-- at the drive-- at the driveway for the-- to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my mother came back and says, I think you better take that helmet off.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You look like you serve in the Jewish brigade.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, that-- they had a Jewish brigade in, in, in Palestine then, you know, that was fighting with the British.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I said-- I said that that might not be a good idea to, to, to do this, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "What really had happened-- the reason they did not purposely hit the clinic.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was a-- there was a, a miss-- a big miss bombing raid.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They-- the large--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they were British.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The large-- the, the telephone center for all of Berlin was down the street.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a large building that had all the-- all the switchboards, you know, all the connections for every-- for every telephone connection in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's what they had targeted.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they missed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, it's not like the smart bombs that they have today.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they hit everything around it, including the clinic.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They did not hit purposely.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So-- and then six months later we lost our apartment.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
